{"tid":1503934,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"全民參與編寫抵制名單","createTime":"2019-08-25T06:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:50:20.000Z","uid":260361,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1b171df847d771d11c47d14371d640696fbd68a4","tid":1503934,"uid":260361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民參與編寫抵制名單</span></span><br />\n香港人一向金魚記憶, 奶共賣港賊從來都唔使付出代價。YouTuber 又好, 餐廳又好, 就連扮本土嘅士多都係奶共完共你班友仔又繼續幫襯。 (士多銷量已回復正常)<br />\n最近發現左呢個: <a href=\"http://cnopenrice.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnopenrice.com%2F&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=09aa06f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cnopenrice.com/</a> 每次消費前上去查一下, 抵制到底, 唔好俾人睇死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hzrp3jm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzrp3jm.png&h=ed5c8550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左睇之外, 更歡迎舉報。特別係要將佢地奶共嘅言行貼出黎, 唔好等佢以為賣完港仲可以繼續做香港人生意。<br />\n<br />\n愛國UCC 正式上榜<br />\n<a href=\"http://cnopenrice.com/index.php/listing/mellow-brown-coffee-by-ucc-sogo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnopenrice.com%2Findex.php%2Flisting%2Fmellow-brown-coffee-by-ucc-sogo%2F&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=85ebce66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cnopenrice.com/index.php/listing/mellow-brown-coffee-by-ucc-sogo/</a><br />\n友口馥 愛國上榜<br />\n<a href=\"http://cnopenrice.com/index.php/listing/friendly-tasty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnopenrice.com%2Findex.php%2Flisting%2Ffriendly-tasty%2F&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=8049c184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cnopenrice.com/index.php/listing/friendly-tasty/</a>"},{"pid":"e68632e926c8481cb242b79d4a24921f19147e8a","tid":1503934,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:38:07.000Z","msg":"(正經)(請給我長期